          So the total ways of drawing is given by 
          <me>
            \left(  ^3C_1 \times ^6C_2 \right) +  \left(  ^3C_2 \times ^6C_1 \right) +  \left(  ^3C_3 \times ^6C_0 \right) = ----
          </me>
          As each case is a complete task.
         </p>
  </solution>
</example>


